### Hadith 2:679

*Narrated Zaid bin Aslam that his father said:*

"I saw 'Umar bin Al-Khattab kissing the Black Stone and he then said,
(to it) 'Had I not seen Allah's Apostle kissing you, (stone) I would not
have kissed you.' "

